Package: numbr
Type: Package
Title: Utility functions for working with numbers
Version: 0.5
Date: 2018-03-08
Authors@R: c(person("Thomas","Hopper",email = "tomhopper@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre")))
Description: Basic mathematical operations, including checking if a vector contains IEEE-754 integers, 
  calculating the geometric mean of a vector, determining the modal value of a vector, extracting the
  mantissa and exponent of a number. Finally, provides a function for converting numbers into
  their English word equivalent. E.g. 1.23e+9 as "100 billion."
License: LGPL-2.1
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
